title: British National Party (BNP) membership list Nov 2008
description:
Leaked membership list of the British right-wing party, the BNP (British National Party).

Leaked in November 2008, believed to date from late 2007. Includes names, addresses, phone numbers, email addresses, occupation details and membership comments. 

As well as holding discriminatory views on the direction of public policy on immigration and race, these lovely people believe that gay people should be subjected to a policy of "don't ask, don't tell" and that civil partnerships should be banned. 

It's nice to see them out of the closet in their full glory.
